---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Kigali - Rwanda's Vibrant Capital City">
  <Header />
  
  <div style="padding-top: 120px;" class="destination-page">
    <div class="destination-container">
      <span class="destination-label">Capital City</span>
      <h1 class="destination-title">Kigali<br><em>Where Africa Shines</em></h1>
      <div class="destination-image">
        <img src="/images/kigali_city_view_1763982611089.png" alt="Kigali cityscape">
      </div>
      <div class="destination-content">
        <p>Kigali is Africa's cleanest and most modern capital — a city of surprising beauty, extraordinary hospitality, and deep meaning. From the moving Kigali Genocide Memorial to the vibrant Inema Arts Centre and an exploding culinary scene, Kigali demands time beyond a simple transit stop.</p>
        
        <h3>Why Visit Kigali</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>🏛️ Kigali Genocide Memorial — one of Africa's most essential museums</li>
          <li>🎨 Inema Arts Centre & Niyo Arts Gallery — contemporary Rwandan creativity</li>
          <li>🍽️ World-class dining at Meza Malonga, The Hut, and Filini</li>
          <li>🛍️ Kimironko Market — authentic local shopping experience</li>
          <li>🌃 Nightlife in Kiyovu and Kimihurura neighborhoods</li>
          <li>🏔️ Mount Kigali — panoramic city views</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Best Time to Visit</h3>
        <p>Kigali enjoys a pleasant climate year-round. The dry seasons (June-September and December-February) offer the best weather for city exploration. However, Kigali's modern infrastructure makes it enjoyable even during the rainy season.</p>
        
        <div class="info-box">
          <h4>Visa Information</h4>
          <p>Kigali International Airport (KGL) offers e-visa arrivals for most nationalities. Apply online at 
          <a href="/visa">irembo.gov.rw</a> or let us handle the process for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .destination-page {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg);
  }
  .destination-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .destination-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .destination-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .destination-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .destination-image {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .destination-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }
  .destination-content {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--ink-light);
  }
  .destination-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .destination-content ul {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  .destination-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .info-box {
    background: var(--bg-off);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .info-box h4 {
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .info-box a {
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .destination-page {
      padding: 5rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>